      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1620188467120-5042ed1eb5da?fm=jpg&q=80&w=1400&auto=format&fit=max&ixlib=rb-4.1.0" alt="Gym with barbell and weight plates — structured training environment" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:10px;" loading="lazy">
      <figcaption style="margin-top:8px;font-size:0.85rem;color:#94a3b8;">A structured session: warm-up → activation → main lifts → accessory → cool-down. Photo: Unsplash (Free to use)</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </section>

